r clients informed about the markets and their portfolio throughout the year we are relentless in our effort to understand the markets their inherent risks and to managing our portfolio strategies responsibly based upon this knowledge it is our job to navigate these complexities in order to help our clients safely reach their longterm financial goals       vision   global perspective you need a firm that understands what’s going on in the world and how it affects your financial objectives   national presence with offices in some of the nation’s largest metropolitan areas we’re there for you when you need us   personal guidance we provide the personal attention of a boutique firm with the comprehensive resources of a large firm     values   objectivity we are fiduciary and advise carefully in order to act in your best interest we actually work for you   transparency we are a feeonly federally registered investment adviser our interests  your interests   longterm planning we create wealth management plans that go beyond your needs today we cant know what will happen tomorrow but we like to be prepared for what might jeffrey powell founder  managing partner polaris greystone financial group jeffs bio » todd moss cfp® cofounder  senior partner polaris greystone financial group todds bio » history of our firm behind every great name is a great story            prev next jeffrey powell founds polaris equity management inc   polaris equity management increases to  million in assets under management   polaris wealth advisers llc is formed   polaris wealth advisers opens an office in houston tx   polaris wealth advisers opens an office in irvine ca   polaris wealth advisers named to the financial times  top registered investment advisers polaris wealth advisers moves its offices from san francisco to san rafael ca polaris wealth advisers surpasses  million in assets under management   polaris wealth advisers llc and greystone financial group inc combine efforts and begin ope