ad gen and nurturing strategy in late  polaris wealth advisors merged with greystone financial group a detroit based wealth management group tea worked closely with the leadership of the two firms to rename brand launch and promote the new firm as polaris greystone financial group across all client touchpoints special attention was given to the need for business continuity across both firm’s existing client base and prospecting efforts   additional projects polaris wealth advisers and greystone financial group combine forming a leading regional polaris wealth advisers and greystone financial group combine forming a leading regional investment advisory firm  the new polaris greystone financial group will manage nearly  billion through offices in california texas and michigan  oct    et from polaris greystone financial group llc san rafael calif and troy mich oct   prnewswire  polaris greystone financial group llc pgfg an investment advisory firm with nearly  billion in client assets under management has been formed through the combination of polaris wealth advisers llc and greystone financial group inc the companies announced today the newly formed group is dedicated to providing superior wealth management and retirement planning services to high net worth families and business owners polaris greystone financial group serves clients through offices in the san francisco southern california houston and detroit metropolitan areas the firm currently operates two divisions polaris greystone wealth management provides financial planning and investment management for individual high net worth families polaris greystone retirement services offers retirement plan solutions and services to plan sponsors and participants within their plans polaris and greystone can trace their corporate roots back to  and  respectively jeffrey j powell polaris founder remains chief executive officer managing partner and chief investment officer of the combined firm todd r moss cofounder of greystone is now president and senior partner of pgfg and will help manage the firms daytoday operations  the combination of polaris and greystone brings together two wellestablished investment advisory firms and enhances our ability to provide superior wealth management and retirement planning services said jeff powell we share the same values and commitment to our clients and together we can offer a broader portfolio of solutions to high net worth families and private businesses through a larger team of talented professionals we are excited by the opportunity to build on the pgfg platform to expand our services and extend into other key wealth markets throughout the united states in todays challenging financial services marketplace investment advisors need greater scale to deliver a full range of resources to clients noted todd moss by joining forces polaris and greystone will have the critical mass to provide an enhanced range of products attract talented employees and support our business with the right technology and systems we are enthusiastic about our ability to grow as a unified firm while maintaining our tradition of excellent wealth management services going forward polaris greystone financial group is well positioned to expand its investment advisory services and geographic reach prior to the combination polaris was named to the financial times  top registered investment advisors the firms core competencies are highly complementary for example polaris has strong money management capabilities and greystone offers customized k plans both firms also have cultivated significant referral relationships polaris greystone will continue greystones longstanding relationship with doeren mayhew a national accounting firm with offices in michigan texas and florida and will continue participating in a national discount brokerage firms referral program about polaris greystone financial group llc polaris greystone financial group llc pgfg is an independently owned registered investment advisory ria firm with offices in san rafael california san francisco troy michigan detroit houston texas and irvine california pgfg is committed to providing superior wealth management services through two investment advisory divisions the largest is pgfgs wealth management services group which provides comprehensive financial planning and portfolio management to high net worth families throughout the united states pgfgs growing retirement plan services group works with business owners throughout the country to navigate the challenging and changing defined contribution and defined benefits marketplace polaris greystone financial group llc is a delaware series llc   source polaris greystone financial group llc view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it join pr newswire for journalists to access all of the free services designated to make your job easier in need of subject matter experts for your story submit a free profnet request and find the sources you need learn more jun    et preview polaris greystone financial group named to  financial times  top registered investment advisers my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distribution platform sign up to get started request more information have an account log in search searching for your content advanced search